OL,3,CBaby dies and family seriously injured
OL,4,Cafter incident in Lanzarote
OL,6,FA baby has died and family members
OL,7,Fseriously injured after a car
OL,8,Fallegedly struck them while walking to
OL,9,Ftheir holiday complex in Lanzarote.
OL,11,FThe family, understood to be from
OL,12,FSouth Shields on South Tyneside, were
OL,13,Fenjoying a break to Playa Blanca on
OL,14,Fthe south coast of the Balearic
OL,15,Fisland, when shortly after 6pm on
OL,16,FMonday 11 March, a driver allegedly
OL,17,Fmounted the pavement and struck
OL,18,Fseveral pedestrians.
OL,20,FThe newborn was pronounced dead at the
OL,21,Fscene.
