OL,6,FThe parents and grandparents were also
OL,7,Famong those seriously injured,
OL,8,Falongside two Swedish nationals. It is
OL,9,Funderstood two people remain in
OL,10,Fintensive care at a hospital in the
OL,11,Fcapital Arrecife.
OL,13,FThe driver has been confirmed as a 23-
OL,14,Fyear-old British woman, who has been
OL,15,Farrested and released on bail while
OL,16,Fenquiries continue.
OL,18,FCourt proceedings were due to start on
OL,19,FWednesday 13 March, but were postponed
OL,20,Fafter the woman allegedly suffered a
OL,21,F"panic attack" in the courtroom.
