OL,3,CBaby dies and family seriously injured
OL,4,Cafter incident in Lanzarote
OL,6,FThe woman is not in custody but has
OL,7,Fforfeited her passport to authorities
OL,8,Fand is forbidden to leave the island.
OL,10,FITV Tyne Tees spoke to Gazette Life
OL,11,Feditor Shaun Addison, an English
OL,12,Fpublication on Lanzarote who has been
OL,13,Freporting on the incident.
OL,15,FMr Addison said there was a "shocked
OL,16,Fsilence" on the island following
OL,17,Fconfirmation of the serious conditions
OL,18,Fof the family and the death of a child.
