OL,6,FHe said the area is popular with
OL,7,FBritish tourists and there has been
OL,8,Fwidespread sadness at the incident but
OL,9,Fpsychological support and assistance
OL,10,Fwas offered in the immediate aftermath
OL,11,Fto witnesses and members of the
OL,12,Fpublic, as well as emergency services
OL,13,Fthat responded to the crash.
OL,15,Freported the Mayor of Yaiza, Oscar
OL,16,FNoda, declared two days of mourning in
OL,17,Fthe days following the incident, with
OL,18,Fa minute's silence in front of the
OL,19,FAyuntamiento building and flags flown
OL,20,Fat half mast.
