OL,6,FSpeaking to Radio Lanzarote-Onda Cero,
OL,7,Fthe publication said Noda stated that
OL,8,F"the images were quite chilling".
OL,10,FAfter receiving an alert about the
OL,11,Ftragedy, Noda stated: "During the
OL,12,Fcall, by the tone of voice and the way
OL,13,Fhe (Head of the Security and Emergency
OL,14,FConsortium, Enrique Espinosa) spoke to
OL,15,Fme I knew that the situation looked
OL,16,Fdrastic."
OL,18,FNoda stated that the event has shocked
OL,19,Fthe whole island and that "we have not
OL,20,Fseen anything similar for a long time".
