OL,6,FIn a statement, the Foreign Office
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are supporting several
OL,8,FBritish nationals following an
OL,9,Fincident in Spain and are in contact
OL,10,Fwith the local authorities."
OL,12,FITV News Tyne Tees has contacted
OL,13,Fpolice in Playa Blanca who said the
OL,14,Fincident is one of an extremely
OL,15,Fsensitive nature but further details
OL,16,Fwill be released in due course.
